<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٦٢ -<span class="c5"> ومنها:</span> يُبَادِرُنِي وَأُبَادِرُهُ،<span class="c5"> حَتَّى يَقُولَ:</span> دَعِي لِي.<span class="c5"> وَأَقُولُ أَنَا:</span> دَعْ لِي <span class="c2">(١)</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
